segment.source: The Microsoft Application Virtualization (App-V) system provides the capability to make applications available to end user computers without having to install the applications directly on those computers.
segment.target: The Microsoft Application Virtualization (App-V) system provides the capability to make applications available to end user computers without having to install the applications directly on those computers.

segment.source: The following online help documentation provides step-by-step procedures for interacting with and using the key system components.
segment.target: The following online help documentation provides step-by-step procedures for interacting with and using the key system components.
